 up to equivalence relations\ngenerated by both usual and extended equivalence groups. Equivalence with\nrespect to these groups and correct choice of gauge coefficients of equations\nplay the major role for simple and clear formulation of the final results.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 25 Jan 2011 09:29:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-01-17"}
